OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,8,Fthe disappearance of teenager Taylor
OL,9,FCharlton in Barnstaple.
OL,11,FThe arrest was made at an address in
OL,12,Fthe North Devon area on Friday 12 June
OL,13,Fafter new information was reported to
OL,14,Fthe police.
OL,16,FThe suspect currently remains in
OL,17,Fpolice custody. Taylor, 15, remains
OL,18,Fmissing. He was last seen on the night
OL,19,Fof Friday 8 May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
