FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,FEnquiries are continuing at a number
OL,7,Fof locations as part of the
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FSenior Investigation Officer Detective
OL,11,FInspector Charlotte Heath said: "Devon
OL,12,Fand Cornwall Police, supported by
OL,13,Fspecialists from neighbouring forces,
OL,14,Fhave committed extensive resources to
OL,15,Ffinding Taylor over the last five
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,26,@sD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,F"Sadly, despite this, his whereabouts
OL,7,Fremain unknown. Much of the
OL,8,Finformation we have gathered does not
OL,9,Findicate the involvement of a third-
OL,10,Fparty.
OL,12,F"This week, we have received new
OL,13,Finformation that someone may have been
OL,14,Finvolved in harming Taylor and, as a
OL,15,Fresult, we have taken action to fully
OL,16,Funderstand this.
OL,18,F"That has included the arrest today of
OL,19,Fa male and his subsequent police
OL,20,Finterview. Taylor's family have been
OL,21,Finformed of this development.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,F"This remains one line of enquiry,
OL,7,Famid many, and we will leave no stone
OL,8,Funturned.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are very much with his
OL,11,Ffamily and friends at this difficult
OL,12,Ftime."
OL,14,FSector Inspector Andy Wills added: "We
OL,15,Fremain committed to find answers for
OL,16,FTaylor's loved-ones and fully
OL,17,Fassessing and acting upon any new
OL,18,Fintelligence that comes to light as
OL,19,Fpart of this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@FO]vD@dOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,F"We remain open-minded and all lines
OL,7,Fof enquiry will be thoroughly reviewed
OL,8,Fin order to ensure we understand, as
OL,9,Ffar as we are able, what has happened
OL,10,Fto Taylor.
OL,12,F"Our officers are working tirelessly
OL,13,Fto ensure this, and all, relevant
OL,14,Flines of enquiry are fully
OL,15,Finvestigated.
OL,17,F"We know how upsetting and concerning
OL,18,Fthis news will be for Taylor's family,
OL,19,Ffriends, and the wider community.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,F"Taylor's family continue to be
OL,7,Fupdated and supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,F"We are asking members of the public
OL,11,Fto help us by avoiding speculation,
OL,12,Fespecially sharing any unconfirmed
OL,13,Finformation online, and allowing
OL,14,Fdetectives to continue our
OL,15,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
