OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781619074
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,Cconnection with missing teenager
OL,6,FThe last confirmed sighting of Taylor
OL,7,Fis on CCTV near a footpath close to
OL,8,FTarka Leisure Centre and the Seven
OL,9,FBrethren car park, Barnstaple, at
OL,10,F10.41pm on Friday 8 May. He is seen
OL,11,Fheading in the direction of the River
OL,12,FTaw.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
